    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="mid">
          <div class="desc">
            <h2>Tanesha's touch, your perfect finish.</h2>
            <p>
              Indulge in a luxurious pampering experience at Tanesha's Nail Spa.
              Our expert nail technician, Tanesha, offers a range of services
